These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different games are played: canasta, billiard, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Game   | canasta | billiard | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, entrepreneur, freelancer
1. the entrepreneur is on the far left or far right##3
2. the freelancer is in the middle##1
3. the freelancer is on the right of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Job   | manager | freelancer | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Pet   | frog | goldfish | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
3 different games are played: billiard, go, scrabble
1. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Game   | billiard | go | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, august, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Birthday   | may | august | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, firefighter, software-developer
1. the software-developer is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
2. the software-developer is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the firefighter is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Job   | security-guard | firefighter | software-developer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, fantasy
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | sports | fantasy |

