.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, tram, helicopter
1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##2
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Transport   | tram | helicopter | taxi |

