.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-15::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, tiparillo, dunhill
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |  2  |     3      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | dunhill | dannemann |

